{"tid":866793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三匪爆食肆掠$2,000","createTime":"2018-10-18T07:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T07:27:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe51746f3ccb74766df524dace504728f2bba5f3","tid":866793,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:04:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181018/20524529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181018%2F20524529&d=1VW3aCcIKcO1RNMqTwAeg2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5f32f655\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181018%2F20524529&h=9084a68a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181018/20524529</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月18日 <br />\n<br />\n三匪爆食肆掠$2,000<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181018/large/a0604a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181018%2Flarge%2Fa0604a.gif&h=1fb396c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n閉路電視拍到竊匪搜掠收銀機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角廣東道一間食肆，昨凌晨遭「竊匪3人組」撬毀電閘掣潛入爆竊，損失2,000元現金。警方正根據店內天眼拍攝到的賊人容貌追緝竊匪歸案。<br />\n<br />\n遇竊的食肆位於廣東道1040號地下，店內及門口均裝有閉路電視。昨晨9時許，63歲姓葉職員返回開舖時，發現大門電閘掣被撬毀，店內有搜掠過痕迹，懷疑遇竊立即致電報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場調查，翻看店舖的閉路電視錄影片段，相信竊匪有3人，於昨日凌晨1時許，撬毀店外的電閘掣後打開捲閘潛入爆竊，其中一名戴帽賊人進入舖內，撬開收銀機搜掠現金，另外兩名賊人則在門外把風。<br />\n<br />\n賊人在店內搜掠完後，通知門外同黨打開捲閘，然後挾贓逃去。食肆負責人經點算，證實損失2,000元。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁澤岡  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n的士被壓　客棄行李<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n地王流標林鄭反擊地產商　稱不會賤賣諷「佢哋睇市好獨特」"},{"pid":"aa67b8aabf0eb5ddd0b66ed9b1b2b4b41ea6f8f2","tid":866793,"uid":17802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"$2000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b648170134b036b17da7369144f31ab29a95a1","tid":866793,"uid":67325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"$2000？大生意嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb9e6e02ad3bb50009163dea08d10cb061e016e","tid":866793,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"開一晚夜 2000蚊, 3人分 一人666<br />\n好似有d做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd67fb321b0cf515660ef08d905c30b2697236d","tid":866793,"uid":73,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"去拆一晚櫃都執1000 啦<br />\n爆格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8afd0a3761f745de0660bfcd2f786d08e8e797","tid":866793,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"2000都除時報大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}